<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA66">
<l>kāyntiruḷai māṟṟik katirilaku māmaṇika</l>
<l>ḷēynta paṇakkatirmēl vevvuyirppa – vāynta</l>
<l>matukai ṭavarum vayiṟuruki māṇṭā</l>
<l>ratukē ṭavarkkiṟuti yāṅku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When you, hotly dispelling darkness, breathed on the rays</l>
<l>of the cobra’s hood that resembles big sapphires shining with rays,</l>
<l>the approaching Matu and Kaiṭavar<note xml:lang="en" place="foot">The two Asuras Madhu and Kaiṭabha were killed by Viṣṇu for trying to steal the Vedas from Brahmā.</note> died, [their] bellies melting.</l>
<l>That was the ruin, thus the end, of those.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
